#External Instruction Sources of Lab Instructions

- Lab on Demand allows you to set Azure Devops (ADO) or GitHub as an instruction source
- This allows for industry standard methods to achieve Source (Version) Control of the lab instructions
- This entire page of instructions is sourced from GitHub!

#### [Click here to learn more about External Instruction Source.](https://docs.learnondemandsystems.com/lod/instruction-source.md)

#### [Click here to view the source code!](https://github.com/tony5a/Virtual_Lab_Demo/blob/master/LOD_External_Instructions)
